# The `WebAssemblyAsmPrinter.cpp` File Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

This file contains a printer that converts from our internal representation of machine-dependent LLVM code to the <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/webassembly">WebAssembly</a> assembly language. <a href="#details">More...</a>
